-- Elbit Imaging Advances Most in Week on Hotels Sale Accord
-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 2012-04-01T08:21:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-01/elbit-imaging-advances-most-in-week-on-hotels-sale-accord.html
  Elbit Imaging Ltd. (EMIT)  advanced the
most in almost a week after the real estate investor said it
will post a gain of about 180 million shekels ($48.5 million)
from the sale of four hotels in the Netherlands.  The  shares  advanced 6.2 percent, the most since March 26,
to 10.16 shekels at 10:41 in  Tel Aviv , giving the company a
market value of 254 million shekels.  Elbit Imaging said a unit has entered into an agreement to
sell a stake in four hotels in the Netherlands to PPHE Hotel
Group Ltd.  To contact the reporter on this story:
